[thinking] **Considering class loading issues**
[thinking] 
[thinking] I'm thinking about how code sources are managed in JVM, specifically regarding the location of binaries. If I'm using a binary with URLClassLoader, I see ClassNotFoundException instead of a general Error when things go wrong. I wonder if testing with a child loader would only catch Errors. Ultimately, I need to remember that native loading might fail with Class.forName, leading to a ClassNotFoundException. This is definitely a bit complex!
